    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "calling a professional doesn't change the facts though. even if i talk to someone, the universe is still just a cold, indifferent vacuum. there is no \"getting better\" when there's nothing to get better to. it's just an endless cycle of consuming and existing for no reason. it feels more like a trap than a life.",
